    "description": "Murtop 是一款充满动作元素的快节奏街机游戏，仿佛直接取自 80 年代，Dig Dug 与 Bomberman 的邂逅。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148170/extras/55c7937bf0573281f1417ffa8ade771e.poster.avif?t=1734087298\" width=400 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148170/extras/55c7937bf0573281f1417ffa8ade771e.webm?t=1734087298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148170/extras/55c7937bf0573281f1417ffa8ade771e.mp4?t=1734087298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>帮助穆尔蒂用她的炸弹大便技能，从饥饿的鼹鼠的入侵中拯救世界！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148170/extras/d8eba47d1d0ec44f15bd09831ee36393.avif?t=1734087298\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>256 个限时单屏关卡……还有杀戮画面！ 让我们看看你是否能做到。<br></li><li>每 5 个阶段奖励阶段...以及一个秘密奖励阶段！<br></li><li>5 首快节奏的芯片音乐曲目。<br></li><li>在线和本地高分排行榜。<br></li><li>优化用于街机柜机。<br></li><li>很多很多的爆炸！</li></ul><br><strong>技术细节：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>带有漂亮边框的垂直屏幕填补了空白。<br></li><li>16 种调色板。<br></li><li>像素完美缩放。<br></li><li>CRT 滤光片。<br></li><li>吸引模式（就像旧的街机一样）。<br></li><li>TATE 模式（旋转屏幕来玩游戏）。</li></ul>",
